{"tid":846640,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發現屋企工人姐姐偷野扔佢出街得唔得","createTime":"2018-10-03T14:21:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T16:18:03.000Z","uid":211247,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f6c459d38a40218fcd5c5eb02deef0d5c75c3549","tid":846640,"uid":211247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T14:21:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如例<br />\n發現左屋企新請嘅工人姐姐偷左老人家錢<br />\n佢最後肯拎返啲錢出嚟,但唔想留佢係屋企<br />\n唔想搞大佢,如果扔曬佢啲野出街趕走佢得唔得<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60bb60fa4a0d6ee48d0b0cc5944e50ce7f2d29a7","tid":846640,"uid":21558,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T14:30:16.000Z","msg":"如果唔係膠post<br />\n<br />\n你一定快啲採取行動<br />\n呢班工主好撚古惑㗎<br />\n打電話去agent講哂成件事<br />\n計好哂啲人工同準備好機票<br />\n就可以炒人<br />\n記得全程拍片<br />\n臨走要check bag<br />\n<br />\n你就咁趕佢走係無用<br />\n佢地工會好撚勁<br />\n會兇鳩你無理解僱"},{"pid":"bbb3782f65582c4d90e0406fa7c0a89c2b04cf3f","tid":846640,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T14:31:15.000Z","msg":"放上黑名單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"143aff83ce2bb9837cde3c17ca53033610905784","tid":846640,"uid":21558,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T14:32:45.000Z","msg":"之後可以寄信去入境處<br />\n講明呢個工人犯乜事<br />\n清清楚楚寫明佢既事<br />\n入境處會特別備註呢個工人既工作簽證<br />\n冇咁容易再批佢落來香港打工"},{"pid":"30a7815257f6a33734d7147fb572be83560f6ca5","tid":846640,"uid":21558,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"60bb60fa4a0d6ee48d0b0cc5944e50ce7f2d29a7","tid":846640,"uid":21558,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T14:30:16.000Z","msg":"如果唔係膠post<br />\n<br />\n你一定快啲採取行動<br />\n呢班工主好撚古惑㗎<br />\n打電話去agent講哂成件事<br />\n計好哂啲人工同準備好機票<br />\n就可以炒人<br />\n記得全程拍片<br />\n臨走要check bag<br />\n<br />\n你就咁趕佢走係無用<br />\n佢地工會好撚勁<br />\n會兇鳩你無理解僱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T14:36:13.000Z","msg":"補充<br />\n轉自網上資料，樓主最好睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n俾工人簽收好晒錢同機票，送佢出門口，就各不相干。佢有手有脚，話之佢去邊<br />\n<br />\n機票最好問清楚佢要邊日，confirm 簽名，即買，所有嘢settle 咗，先好放佢走，唔好話再约，佢唔出現，有排煩<br />\n<br />\n如佢話要錢唔要機票，都可以，要佢寫張纸自己要求，錄埋影<br />\n<br />\n簽收:<br />\n1) 當月工資，計到炒佢嗰日<br />\n2) 未放大假錢<br />\n3) 機票，或錢代替<br />\n4) $100交通津貼<br />\n5) 一個月代通知金"},{"pid":"9a380d4bb6974cbb78ce892d2c7abcf5b88c13c9","tid":846640,"uid":211247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"143aff83ce2bb9837cde3c17ca53033610905784","tid":846640,"uid":21558,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T14:32:45.000Z","msg":"之後可以寄信去入境處<br />\n講明呢個工人犯乜事<br />\n清清楚楚寫明佢既事<br />\n入境處會特別備註呢個工人既工作簽證<br />\n冇咁容易再批佢落來香港打工"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T14:37:11.000Z","msg":"thank you ching<br />\n錄左片 但佢唔肯走<br />\n仲兇我地唔可以扔佢啲野<br />\n如果我真係扔左佢出街會唔會比人告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24349da151cb2d681a9231c0db2d31ff54f409d1","tid":846640,"uid":21558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9a380d4bb6974cbb78ce892d2c7abcf5b88c13c9","tid":846640,"uid":211247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"143aff83ce2bb9837cde3c17ca53033610905784","tid":846640,"uid":21558,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T14:32:45.000Z","msg":"之後可以寄信去入境處<br />\n講明呢個工人犯乜事<br />\n清清楚楚寫明佢既事<br />\n入境處會特別備註呢個工人既工作簽證<br />\n冇咁容易再批佢落來香港打工"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T14:37:11.000Z","msg":"thank you ching<br />\n錄左片 但佢唔肯走<br />\n仲兇我地唔可以扔佢啲野<br />\n如果我真係扔左佢出街會唔會比人告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T14:41:16.000Z","msg":"佢冇得唔走<br />\n被炒工人有權留港14日<br />\n14日後點都要走<br />\n反正你要買機票，你問定佢要乜日子<br />\n如果佢唔要機票改要錢<br />\n你就照俾佢<br />\n但要白紙黑字要佢簽收，全程拍片<br />\n<br />\n佢呢段期間可以去agent度<br />\nAgent實有地方俾佢地住"},{"pid":"be3f62fa099a1ff6430138fe43ad424bf180dc6f","tid":846640,"uid":15945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T14:41:20.000Z","msg":"平時淨係識得爭取強加最低工資同匯錢返鄉下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acbfcfa7c2aad4cea2366b75bff3859fd094f01a","tid":846640,"uid":3167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T14:44:12.000Z","msg":"買條狗鏈鎖起佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"770ab2282f85f3f88fd6d0e2c7009392ca78ded7","tid":846640,"uid":211247,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T14:48:09.000Z","msg":"叫佢即時簽辭職信唔比代通知金得唔得?<br />\n唔想咁衰斷人衣食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2e2da8c03b4972043128ebf9c7ca32143cb2376","tid":846640,"uid":21483,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"770ab2282f85f3f88fd6d0e2c7009392ca78ded7","tid":846640,"uid":211247,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T14:48:09.000Z","msg":"叫佢即時簽辭職信唔比代通知金得唔得?<br />\n唔想咁衰斷人衣食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T14:50:42.000Z","msg":"第一你唔俾代通知金人，你無証明佢犯錯你有問題，再者做出呢啲野你留地雷俾下手，你都幾抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"522a8f5953667039fe26d62b684835879433ab75","tid":846640,"uid":21558,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"770ab2282f85f3f88fd6d0e2c7009392ca78ded7","tid":8466